headline.print_headline: Timeline of the California Bank Robbery and Chase
headline.main: Timeline of the California Bank Robbery and Chase

lead_paragraph: At 2:11 p.m. on Wednesday, police in the California city of Stockton received a report of a bank robbery in progress, police said. What follows is a summary by police of the subsequent hour-long chase and furious gunbattle that ended in the deaths of two suspects and a hostage.
